---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects | Hashir Khan | AI Automation & Agentic Workflows" description="Real-world AI agent deployments: lead enrichment, appointment scheduling, 24/7 customer support, and custom assistant integrations.">
	<section class="page-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Recent case studies<span class="period">.</span></h1>
			<p>Real deployments where we replaced manual workflows with autonomous agent systems. Results that speak for themselves.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section-padding">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="projects-grid">
				<div class="card-marketing project-card reveal-on-scroll">
					<div class="card-icon-container">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="22 3 2 3 10 12.46 10 19 14 21 14 12.46 22 3"></polygon></svg>
					</div>
					<span class="card-meta-tag mono">CASE_01 // LEAD_ENRICHMENT</span>
					<h3>Automated Lead Enrichment Pipeline</h3>
					<p>Replaced 3 manual researcher roles with an agent that takes CRM leads, enriches them via company APIs, scores purchase intent, and pushes qualified leads into the sales queue. Processing 200+ leads/month with 92% accuracy.</p>
					<div class="project-metrics">
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">26h</span><span class="metric-label">weekly saved</span></div>
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">3×</span><span class="metric-label">faster close</span></div>
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">92%</span><span class="metric-label">accuracy</span></div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="card-marketing project-card reveal-on-scroll">
					<div class="card-icon-container">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
					</div>
					<span class="card-meta-tag mono">CASE_02 // SCHEDULING</span>
					<h3>WhatsApp Appointment Booking Agent</h3>
					<p>An agent that books appointments entirely within WhatsApp — checks availability, resolves conflicts, sends Calendar invites, and follows up 24 hours prior. Reduced no-shows by 40% for a health services provider.</p>
					<div class="project-metrics">
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">40%</span><span class="metric-label">fewer no-shows</span></div>
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">∞</span><span class="metric-label">self-serve booking</span></div>
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">3min</span><span class="metric-label">avg booking</span></div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="card-marketing project-card reveal-on-scroll">
					<div class="card-icon-container">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<span class="card-meta-tag mono">CASE_03 // SUPPORT</span>
					<h3>24/7 Customer Support Agent</h3>
					<p>Trained on full product knowledge base, this agent answered 85% of incoming tickets autonomously in under 30 seconds, escalating only complex edge cases to human agents. Maintained 4.9★ satisfaction throughout.</p>
					<div class="project-metrics">
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">85%</span><span class="metric-label">auto-resolved</span></div>
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">&lt;30s</span><span class="metric-label">response time</span></div>
						<div class="metric-chip"><span class="metric-value">4.9★</span><span class="metric-label">satisfaction</span></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
